# This is a placeholder for LiberationSans-Regular.ttf or any other default font.
# For the script to work without a real font file here, the _get_font_path function
# will need to successfully find a system font or have a fallback mechanism.
# If you have the actual LiberationSans-Regular.ttf, place it here.
# On many Linux systems, it might be found at /usr/share/fonts/truetype/liberation/LiberationSans-Regular.ttf
